<p>i have a long list of open questions, a lot of ideas for how to handle different things, and no clear picture as to how feasible any of this is going to end up being. but i’m taking it a piece at a time, just enjoying the journey and the learning experience.</p>
<p>the way i see it there are only three things stopping me:</p>
<ul>
